title: How To Quit Your Day Job And Be A Full Time Comedian
description:
Enjoy!

This comes courtesy of a scammer who rips people off with shady subpar comedy classes.

It's pure junk information, and most of it past that point is just common sense. Why pay for the usual crap you find in strip mall meet ups to "make money from your own home" When you can download it for free?

Pass it along, take money out of the scammers mouth... After all, he does the same daily to folks, stealing their money and providing nothing of value in return
